Nakoresheje umubiri mpamagara izina rya Yesu.

0:08:23.360,0:08:29.580
Dukoresha umubiri cyane mu bintu byo mu mwuka.

0:08:29.580,0:08:35.540
Rimwe ucana buji, rizamurika - yitereke.

0:08:35.540,0:08:41.980
Ntabwo mushobora gucana buji, na none ngo mwongere muyicane... oya.

0:08:41.980,0:08:44.660
Kuva itazimye, ntabwo iba yazimye.

